{
  "texts": [
    "**postLinks**: This table keeps track of links between posts.",
    "Each entry has a unique post link ID, creation date, post ID, related post ID, and link type ID.",
    "The link type ID specifies the nature of the link between the posts. 2.",
    "**postHistory**: This table records the history of edits or changes made to posts.",
    "It includes information such as the post history ID, post history type ID, post ID, revision globally unique ID (GUID), creation date of the edit, user ID of the editor, detailed content of the post after the edit, comments on the edit, and the editor's display name. 3."
  ]
}